Body: Possible Duplicate:  “Insufficient storage” when trying to install anything on htc thunderbolt  When I download the Go Launcher Ex App from the play store, it downloads okay but shows "Insufficient memory"(The internal memory) when it tries to install it. :/It is a 6 or 7Mb app, where as my internal storage has 25Mb free and the SDCard has almost 1Gb free space. Title: Insufficient space when downloading Go Launcher EX?

history.Text: When I download the Go Launcher Ex App from the play store, it downloads okay but shows "Insufficient memory"(The internal memory) when it tries to install it.... :/It is a 6 or 7 mb app where as my internal storage has 25mb free and the sd card has almost 1Gb free space. I don't get what the problem is.Would really appreciate it if someone helped me. :)Thanks.Nihal Chowdhury, Bangladesh.
